 313:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \brief
 314:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Runs built-in self-tests specified by the test enable mask.
 315:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 316:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \details
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ash750\AppData\Local\Temp\cchIVX1d.s 			page 7


 317:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  The function performs various self-tests on all enabled widgets
 318:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  and sensors in the Component. The required set of tests can be selected
 319:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  using the bit-mask in the testEnMask parameter.
 320:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 321:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Use CapSense_TST_RUN_SELF_TEST_MASK to execute all the self-tests or
 322:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  any combination of the masks (defined in testEnMask parameter) to specify the
 323:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  test list.
 324:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 325:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  To execute a single-element test (i.e. for one widget or sensor), the following
 326:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  functions are available:
 327:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_CheckGlobalCRC()
 328:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_CheckWidgetCRC()
 329:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_CheckBaselineDuplication()
 330:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_CheckIntegritySensorPins()
 331:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_GetSensorCapacitance()
 332:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_GetShieldCapacitance()
 333:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_GetExtCapCapacitance()
 334:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_GetVdda()
 335:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 336:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Refer to these functions for detail information on a corresponding test.
 337:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 338:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \param testEnMask
 339:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Specifies the tests to be executed. Each bit corresponds to one test. It is
 340:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  possible to launch the function with any combination of the available tests.
 341:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC       - Verifies the RAM structure CRC of global parameters.
 342:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_WDGT_CRC         - Verifies the RAM widget structure CRC for all the widgets.
 343:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_BSLN_DUPLICATION - Verifies the baseline consistency of all the sensors (inverse 
 344:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SNS_SHORT        - Checks all the sensors for a short to GND / VDD / other sensor
 345:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SNS_CAP          - Measures all the sensors capacitance.
 346:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SH_CAP           - Measures the shield capacitance.
 347:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_EXTERNAL_CAP     - Measures the capacitance of the available external capacitors.
 348:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_VDDA             - Measures the Vdda voltage.
 349:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_RUN_SELF_TEST_MASK - Executes all available tests.
 350:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 351:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \return
 352:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Returns a bit-mask with a status of execution of the specified tests:
 353:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CYRET_SUCCESS - All the tests are passed.
 354:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_NOT_EXECUTED - The previously triggered scanning is not
 355:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *    completed.
 356:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_BAD_PARAM - A non-defined test was requested in the
 357:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *    testEnMask parameter.
 358:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC       - Fails the test of the RAM structure CRC of global parameters.
 359:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_WDGT_CRC         - Fails the test of the RAM widget structure CRC of any widget.
 360:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_BSLN_DUPLICATION - Fails the baseline consistency test of any sensor.
 361:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SNS_SHORT        - Fails the test of the short to GND or VDD of any sensor.
 362:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SNS_CAP          - Fails the execution of any sensor capacitance measurement test
 363:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_SH_CAP           - Fails the execution of the shield capacitance measurement test
 364:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_EXTERNAL_CAP     - Fails the execution of any external capacitor capacitance meas
 365:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_VDDA             - Fails the execution of the Vdda voltage measurement test.
 366:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 367:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *******************************************************************************/
