 530:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \brief
 531:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Checks the stored CRC of the CapSense_RAM_STRUCT data structure.
 532:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 533:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \details
 534:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  This function validates the data integrity of the
 535:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  CapSense_RAM_STRUCT data structure by calculating the CRC and
 536:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  comparing it with the stored CRC value (i.e. CapSense_GLB_CRC_VALUE).
 537:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 538:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  If the stored and calculated CRC values differ, the calculated CRC
 539:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  is stored to the CapSense_GLB_CRC_CALC_VALUE register and
 540:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  the CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC bit is set in the
 541:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  CapSense_TEST_RESULT_MASK_VALUE register. The function never
 542:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  clears the CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC bit.
 543:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 544:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  It is recommended to use the CapSense_SetParam() function to
ARM GAS  C:\Users\ash750\AppData\Local\Temp\cchIVX1d.s 			page 11


 545:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  change a value of CapSense_RAM_STRUCT data structure register/elements
 546:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  as CRC is updated by the CapSense_SetParam() function.
 547:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 548:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  This test also can be initiated by using CapSense_RunSelfTest()
 549:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  function with the CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC mask input.
 550:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 551:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** * \return
 552:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  Returns a status of the executed test:
 553:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CYRET_SUCCESS - The stored CRC matches the calculated CRC
 554:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *  - CapSense_TST_GLOBAL_CRC - The stored CRC is wrong.
 555:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *
 556:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** *******************************************************************************/
 557:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** uint32 CapSense_CheckGlobalCRC(void)
 558:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c **** {
