2860:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *  - CapSense_TST_MEASUREMENT_HIGH_LIMIT - The measured capacitance is above th
2861:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                          maximum possible value.
2862:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                          The measurement result is invalid.
2863:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                          It is possible that the sensor was
2864:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                          shorted to GND.
2865:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *  - CapSense_TST_MEASUREMENT_ERROR - an unexpected fault occurred during
2866:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                     the measurement, the measurement may need
