2868:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *
2869:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     * \return
2870:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *  Returns the capacitance of a sensor element in femtofarads. The status
