3524:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                       successfully, the result is valid.
3525:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *  - CapSense_TST_MEASUREMENT_LOW_LIMIT - The measured capacitance is below
3526:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                         the minimum possible value.
3527:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                     *                                         The measurement result is invalid.
