3912:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *
3913:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 * \details
3914:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  The function connect an external capacitor (Cmod, Csh, CintA/CintB)
3915:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  to CSD block, defines a modclock frequency divider and an Idac code
3916:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  and measures a capacitance in range of 0,5 to 5,0 nF.
3917:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  If the result exceeds 75 % of a range high bound the function divides modClk,
3918:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  multiply Idac code to the fixed value to wide a measurement range and performs
3919:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  another measuring cycle for a capacitance in range of 5,0 to 60,0 nF.
3920:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  After that the function disconnect the external capacitor, calculate a result
3921:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *  and stores it to a correspondent register of the self-test data structure.
3922:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 *
3923:Generated_Source\PSoC4/CapSense_SelfTest.c ****                 * \param extCapId
